trans-unit.source: Defines the settings for a peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: Define as configurações para um serviço resolvedor de pares.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets the specific settings for a custom peer resolver.
trans-unit.target: Obtém as configurações específicas para um resolvedor de pares personalizado.

trans-unit.source: This property is set only if <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings.Mode%2A> is set to <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode>.
trans-unit.target: Essa propriedade é definida somente se <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings.Mode%2A>for definido como <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode> </xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings.Mode%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref> that contains the settings and resolver instance for the associated custom peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref>que contém as configurações e a instância do resolvedor para o serviço resolvedor de pares personalizado associado.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether the peer resolver instance associated with this service is either PNRP-specific, a custom resolver, or automatically determined.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define se a instância do resolvedor peer associada a esse serviço é específico PNRP, um resolvedor personalizado ou determinado automaticamente.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode"></xref> enumeration value that specifies the mode of the peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode"></xref>valor de enumeração que especifica o modo do serviço resolvedor peer.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the specific referral policy used by the peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define a política de referência específica usada pelo serviço resolvedor peer.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref> that specifies whether peer referrals are shared or not.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref>que especifica se as referências de ponto a ponto são compartilhadas ou não.
